name: Max
description:
Ideal for baby showers, celebrating a birth or a special gift for your new baby. Bootielicious' collection is handmade using designer fabrics and high quality materials. 

You’ll receive: 
A sketch circles blanket, made with 100% cotton with a neutral backing made from 100% flannelette. Measures: 85cm x 98cm.

Blue & white burping cloth, made from 100% cotton and absorbent terry towelling for easy washing. Burping cloth is sized to cover you from any messes while feeding your baby and is a convenient option than using a towel or nappy.

Max knit booties and hat, made with bamboo and wool for ultimate softness and warmth. Size: Newborns - 3 months of age.
